OL,3,CScottish government spends #200m on IT
OL,4,Cconsultants for farming payments
OL,6,FRural Affairs Secretary Mairi Gougeon
OL,7,Fsaid the firms are providing IT
OL,8,Fservices rather than simply consulting
OL,9,Fon how to run the programmes.
OL,11,FBut farmers have raised concerns that
OL,12,Fthe current system is not fit for
OL,13,Fpurpose and that forthcoming changes
OL,14,Fto the payments means the IT could
OL,15,Fbecome obsolete.
