OL,3,CScottish government spends #200m on IT
OL,4,Cconsultants for farming payments
OL,6,FJonnie Hall, director of policy at the
OL,7,FNational Farmers Union of Scotland,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News: "It's a staggering
OL,9,Famount of money and our members `
OL,10,Ffarmers and crofters across Scotland `
OL,11,Fwill be gobsmacked by such amounts of
OL,12,Fmoney going into consultants' fees to
OL,13,Fdeliver agricultural support payments.
OL,15,F"And yet the impression that we have
OL,16,Fabout that IT system has been that it
OL,17,Fwas very much a flawed system from day
OL,18,Fone.
