OL,6,F"It has recovered, it has got back on
OL,7,Ftrack, but if we're still paying
OL,8,Fsignificant amounts of money to keep
OL,9,Fit ticking over then that has got to
OL,10,Fbe a concern for all of us."
OL,12,FFailures in the system led to payments
OL,13,Fto thousands of farmers being delayed,
OL,14,Fwhich led to a damning report in 2017
OL,15,Ffrom Audit Scotland, the financial
OL,16,Fwatchdog.
