OL,3,CScottish government spends #200m on IT
OL,4,Cconsultants for farming payments
OL,6,FJames Playfair-Hannay, a farmer near
OL,7,FKelso, said the IT system "had a lot
OL,8,Fof teething issues when it was
OL,9,Fintroduced. It cost a lot of money, it
OL,10,Fwas over budget, it was late. It's now
OL,11,Fantiquated".
OL,13,FHolyrood's Rural Affairs and Islands
OL,14,Fcommittee has heard evidence in recent
OL,15,Fweeks from the agricultural sector
OL,16,Fthat the IT system is not working for
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,26,@oD@[OUsD@KO]
