OL,3,CScottish government spends #200m on IT
OL,4,Cconsultants for farming payments
OL,6,FAt a session on Wednesday, agriculture
OL,7,Fminister Jim Fairlie said that policy
OL,8,Fwas not being driven by the system's
OL,9,Fcapabilities.
OL,11,FFinlay Carson, the committee's
OL,12,Fconvener and the Conservative MSP for
OL,13,FGalloway and West Dumfries, said the
OL,14,FIT system is "not fit for purpose".
OL,16,FHe called for the Scottish government
OL,17,Fto be "far more transparent" about the
OL,18,Fcosts involved in administering the
OL,19,Fset up.
