OL,6,FThe Scottish government said that its
OL,7,Fagriculture and rural economy
OL,8,Fdirectorate needs several digital
OL,9,Fsystems to operate and that not all of
OL,10,Fthem are to administer payments.
OL,12,FHowever, it said that the nine years
OL,13,Fcovered by the analysis of the
OL,14,Fpayments including the end of the IT
OL,15,Fsystem being built.
OL,17,FIt was originally designed to
OL,18,Fimplement European Union Common
OL,19,FAgricultural Policy payments before
OL,20,Fthe UK left the bloc in 2020.
